'''Diplomat's Valet''' was one of the many stores found on the [[Grand Colonnade]] on [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal]]. The Diplomat's Valet specialized in carrying the latest fashions from [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

